{"barInfo":{"barName":"骁","description":"开放自由的类贴吧式留言板","isMainBar":true,"isPublic":true},"list":[{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>……</p> ","floor":1,"pid":0,"postTime":"2019-03-21 10:07:32","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","sourceUrl":"","tid":2951},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p><img src=\"/xbar/a7f9fb9ca9724f4f34.jpg\"></p> ","floor":2,"pid":8588,"postTime":"2019-03-21 10:14:39","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2951},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>这是最近一周广州市的天气预报，我预计于23日（周六）24日（周日）在广州停留两天。</p> ","floor":3,"pid":8589,"postTime":"2019-03-21 10:15:36","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2951},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>可以看出 周六和周日的天气是小雨转阵雨。显然不算理想的天气。不过我想应该也没什么大碍。</p> ","floor":4,"pid":8590,"postTime":"2019-03-21 10:16:46","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2951},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>最高气温在22度左右，是一个比较舒适的温度。但是实际上我对穿衣没有经验。也许我应该准备两套衣服。准备两种外套和一件薄毛衣。</p> ","floor":5,"pid":8591,"postTime":"2019-03-21 10:20:00","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2951},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>接下来是广州地图，广州还是很大的。</p><p><img src=\"/xbar/67e4c7fce2a4e1eea4.jpg\"></p> ","floor":6,"pid":8592,"postTime":"2019-03-21 10:22:39","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2951},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>我在广州的落脚点是华南师范大学附近，约在广州东站的东侧。</p> ","floor":7,"pid":8593,"postTime":"2019-03-21 10:23:30","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2951},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>根据评估，有几个地方是必须要去的：</p><p>陈家祠、越秀公园、北京路步行街、圣心大教堂、珠江夜游、珠江新城。</p><p>再来几个选去的地方：</p><p>珠江水上巴士、沙面岛、白云公园、华南师范大学。</p><br><p>基本可以把两天排得满满当当的。</p> ","floor":8,"pid":8594,"postTime":"2019-03-21 10:46:21","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2951},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>广州公交的话，支付宝上有羊城通可以使用。</p><p>地铁的话估计只能买票了。</p> ","floor":9,"pid":8595,"postTime":"2019-03-21 10:47:32","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2951},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>我在广州站下车，那里离越秀公园最近。那就先去越秀公园。</p><p>也许第一天就可以把除了珠江新城之外的必去地点走遍。</p> ","floor":10,"pid":8596,"postTime":"2019-03-21 10:50:28","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2951},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>第二天也许可以沙面岛或白云公园二选一。再去珠江新城。</p><p>不过具体行程还有受到陈春燕的影响。</p> ","floor":11,"pid":8597,"postTime":"2019-03-21 10:55:16","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2951},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>周一在深圳玩，就随意一点，不做什么规划了。</p> ","floor":12,"pid":8598,"postTime":"2019-03-21 11:01:03","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2951},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>明天早上去哪吃饭呢</p> ","floor":13,"pid":8599,"postTime":"2019-03-22 14:07:07","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2951}],"pageInfo":{"total":13,"pageSize":30,"current":1},"threadInfo":{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","classifyName":"闲谈","goodClassifyName":"","id":2951,"isGood":true,"isPicture":true,"isRepost":false,"postTime":"2019-03-21 10:07:32","replyCount":13,"title":"尝试认真做出一些规划……","topState":0},"tid":2951,"total":13,"totalPages":1,"viewHost":false,"users":{"admin":{"exists":true,"name":"孙天骁","code":"admin","alias":"stx","description":"一个内心丰富的人","homepageUrl":"/u/stx","group":5,"groupName":"站长","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/s/user/FufL-vSFO5eM1we1mxdfYHKH9tfK.jpg","realName":"孙天骁","refBaike":"","isManager":true,"isMe":true,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-02-11 21:45:00"}},"needVerify":true}